<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich VII. Reuß von Plauen, Herr von Greiz und Hauptmann von Bärnau</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Aufschub des Gerichtstermins in Bärnau von 14 Tagen für Burkhard Sebach, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="5r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_11_r2l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rewſſen von <expan>Plawe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Greucʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l2">vnd <expan>hauptman<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu Pernaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_11_r2l3">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt Burkhart Sebach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l4">vvie daʒ Jr Jm <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> tag auf den <expan>Sun<ex>n</ex>tag</expan> nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frauntag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l5">ſchierſ für ew gen Pernaw <expan>beſcheide<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von habe vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l9">die Er mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_11_line_1574072574732_411">Jn pernaw </ab></add> bekümert hab / Nu ſpricht der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l10"> <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> burger / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">e </del> Jm der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> tag <expan>cʒeſuch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒukürcʒ ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l11">vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">von </del> des von nötlıcher ſache wegen niht <expan>geſuch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l13">vnd hat vns gebeten daʒ vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough">das <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_11_r2l12">ew das </ab></add> alſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l14">
<del rend="strikethrough">vo vnd bit </del> vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell von <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l15">daʒ Jr Jm <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag xiiij tag erlengern wöllet / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l16">Er den <expan>geſuch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müg / vnd alſo <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l17">fleiſſe / daʒ Jr Jm <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag alſo xiiij tag durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r2l18"><expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> erlengern wöllet / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="5r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rewssen von <expan>Plawe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Greucz und
                                <expan>hauptman<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Pernaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Burkhart Sebach,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz ir im <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
              tag auf den <app><note><q type="date"><expan>sun<ex>n</ex>tag</expan> nach <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frauntag
                                    schiers</q>18.08.1409</note></app> für ew gen Pernaw <expan>bescheide<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von habe wegen, die er
            mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten <add>in Pernaw</add> bekümert hab. Nu spricht der
                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan> burger daz im der
              <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> tag <expan>czesuch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
            czukürcz sey und des von nötlicher sache wegen niht <expan>gesuch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
            müg, und hat uns gebeten, daz wir <add>ew das</add> also
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell
            von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllen, daz ir im
                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag xiiii tag erlengern wöllet, daz er den
                <expan>gesuch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müg. Und also <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisse, daz ir
            im <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag also xiiii tag durch
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> erlengern wöllet, als etc. Das
              <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
